Docs.summary: A map from syntax node in the later compilation to syntax node in the previous compilation, or null if is false and the map is not needed or the source of the current method is the same as the source of the previous method.
Docs.remarks: The map does not need to map all syntax nodes in the active method, only those syntax nodes that declare a local or generate a long lived local.
